name: White / Afterlife
description:
Inspired by a song from Efek Rumah Kaca - Putih.

Selamat datang di samudra.
Ombak ombak menerpa.
Rekah rekah dan berkahlah.
Dalam dirinya, terhimpun alam raya semesta.
Dalam jiwanya, berkumpul hangat surga neraka.

Imagination about the afterlife. Something that everyone is curious about.
Where are we after this life?
